label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"鸡毛细线虫病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":8,"end":15,"text":"毛首科毛细线虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"线虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":34,"end":38,"text":"寄生虫病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":24,"end":25,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":26,"end":29,"text":"消化道","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 鸡毛细线虫病是由毛首科毛细线虫属的多种线虫寄生于鸡的消化道引起的一种寄生虫病。

label: [{"start":5,"end":9,"text":"毛细线虫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 不同种类的毛细线虫的寄生部位不同。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"有轮毛细线虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":9,"end":10,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":11,"end":13,"text":"嗦囊","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"食道","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 有轮毛细线虫寄生于鸡的嗦囊和食道；

label: [{"start":0,"end":5,"text":"鸽毛细线虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":8,"end":9,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"小肠","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 鸽毛细线虫寄生于鸡的小肠；

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"膨尾毛细线虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":9,"end":12,"text":"鸡小肠","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 膨尾毛细线虫寄生于鸡小肠。

label: [{"start":2,"end":6,"text":"毛细线虫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 这些毛细线虫形态相似，小者长7~8mm,中等者长20~25mm,最长的可达到60mm,雄虫略小于雌虫。

label: [{"start":0,"end":5,"text":"鸽毛细线虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":37,"end":38,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":44,"end":50,"text":"十二指肠黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":60,"end":62,"text":"肠腔","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 鸽毛细线虫发育是直接进行的，即卵排出体外，在卵壳内发育为第一期幼虫，幼虫被鸡啄食后，进入十二指肠黏膜内，发育为成虫后进入肠腔。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"有轮毛细线虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":7,"end":13,"text":"膨尾毛细线虫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 有轮毛细线虫、膨尾毛细线虫需以蚯蚓为中间宿主。

label: [{"start":34,"end":35,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":56,"end":61,"text":"鸡小肠黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":72,"end":75,"text":"消化道","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 虫卵排出体外发育为含第一期幼虫的卵后，被蚯蚓吞食，发育为第二期幼虫，鸡吞食了这种蚯蚓后而遭受感染，第二期幼虫钻入鸡小肠黏膜中发育为成虫，然后返回消化道。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":4,"end":8,"text":"食欲不振","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":9,"end":13,"text":"精神萎靡","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"消瘦","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"肠炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":21,"end":27,"text":"常作吞咽动作","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":31,"end":33,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":34,"end":37,"text":"成年鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 病鸡表现食欲不振，精神萎靡，消瘦并有肠炎或常作吞咽动作，严重时雏鸡、成年鸡均可引起死亡。

label: [{"start":6,"end":7,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":32,"end":33,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":17,"end":22,"text":"轻度的炎症","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":23,"end":25,"text":"增厚","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":40,"end":42,"text":"炎症","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":43,"end":45,"text":"增厚","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":52,"end":57,"text":"嗦囊壁出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":55,"end":57,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":59,"end":66,"text":"有黏浓性分泌物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":67,"end":71,"text":"黏膜脱落","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":69,"end":71,"text":"脱落","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":72,"end":74,"text":"坏死","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":8,"end":10,"text":"嗦囊","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":11,"end":15,"text":"食道管壁","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":34,"end":36,"text":"嗦囊","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":37,"end":39,"text":"食道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":52,"end":55,"text":"嗦囊壁","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":67,"end":69,"text":"黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 轻度感染时，鸡的嗦囊和食道管壁仅有轻度的炎症和增厚：严重感染时，鸡的嗦囊和食道的炎症和增厚更为明显，甚至嗦囊壁出血，并有黏浓性分泌物和黏膜脱落、坏死等病变。

label: [{"start":2,"end":8,"text":"鸡毛细线虫病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 由于鸡毛细线虫病的虫卵特征性不强，所以诊断时需将临床症状、剖检发现虫体、相应部位的病变以及粪检虫卵结合，才能作出确切的诊断。

label: [{"start":1,"end":7,"text":"鸡毛细线虫病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 对鸡毛细线虫病可选用以下药物进行驱虫。

label: [{"start":19,"end":27,"text":"混入饲料进行饲喂","labels":["control"]},{"start":3,"end":7,"text":"左旋咪唑","labels":["drug"]}]
text: (1)左旋咪唑，按25mg/kg体重，混入饲料进行饲喂。

label: [{"start":3,"end":8,"text":"硫化二苯胺","labels":["drug"]},{"start":45,"end":52,"text":"混入饲料中饲喂","labels":["control"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"小鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":27,"end":30,"text":"成年鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: (2)硫化二苯胺，按小鸡0.3～0.5mg/kg体重，成年鸡0.5~1.0mg/kg体重，混入饲料中饲喂，连喂2天。

label: [{"start":18,"end":24,"text":"一次口服给药","labels":["control"]},{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"噻嘧啶","labels":["drug"]}]
text: (3)噻嘧啶，按60mg/kg体重，一次口服给药。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"加强卫生管理","labels":["control"]},{"start":7,"end":16,"text":"保持鸡舍的清洁卫生","labels":["control"]},{"start":17,"end":23,"text":"及时清除粪便","labels":["control"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"发酵","labels":["control"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"粪便","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 加强卫生管理，保持鸡舍的清洁卫生，及时清除粪便，并进行发酵以杀灭虫卵。

label: [{"start":1,"end":7,"text":"鸡毛细线虫病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":15,"end":20,"text":"预防性驱虫","labels":["control"]}]
text: 在鸡毛细线虫病流行的地区要进行预防性驱虫。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"鸡比翼线虫病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"线虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":21,"end":22,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":23,"end":25,"text":"气管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 鸡比翼线虫病是由比翼科、比翼属的线虫寄生于鸡的气管内引起的。

label: [{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":7,"end":11,"text":"张口呼吸","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":17,"end":20,"text":"开口病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":8,"end":9,"text":"口","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 因其能引起病鸡张口呼吸的症状故又称开口病。

label: [{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":7,"end":10,"text":"成年鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":33,"end":35,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":27,"end":31,"text":"呼吸困难","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":35,"end":39,"text":"窒息死亡","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 主要侵害雏鸡，成年鸡很少发病和死亡，呈地方性流行，常因呼吸困难导致病鸡窒息死亡，对养禽业的危害较大。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"比翼线虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":14,"end":20,"text":"气管比翼线虫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 比翼线虫种类甚多，国内仅发现气管比翼线虫。

label: [{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"红虫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 活虫体呈红色。故有红虫之称。

label: [{"start":41,"end":44,"text":"权子虫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 雄虫以交合伞附着于雌虫位于体前部的阴门处，永成交配状态，从外形看成丫字形，所以又叫权子虫。

label: [{"start":8,"end":12,"text":"比翼线虫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 虫卵两端有卵塞。比翼线虫属直接发育型。

label: [{"start":3,"end":4,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"气管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":14,"end":18,"text":"气管黏液","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"口腔","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 雌虫在鸡的气管中产卵，虫卵随气管黏液进入口腔，或咳出；

label: [{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"消化道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"粪便","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 或咽入消化道随粪便排出体外，在适宜的条件下，发育为第三期幼虫，含幼虫的卵在土壤中可存活8~9个月。

label: [{"start":9,"end":10,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":21,"end":22,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 可通过3条途径感染鸡：一是感染性虫卵直接被鸡吞食；

label: [{"start":8,"end":9,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 二是孵出的幼虫被鸡啄食；

label: [{"start":37,"end":38,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 三是感染性虫卵被贮藏宿主吞食(在其体内不发育),贮藏宿主包括蚯蚓、蛄蝓等，鸡吞食了受感染的贮藏宿主而感染。

label: [{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"肠壁","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"心脏","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"肺肺","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":22,"end":24,"text":"气管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 幼虫钻入肠壁，随血流移行至心脏、肺肺，最后在气管发育为成虫。

label: [{"start":35,"end":39,"text":"隐性感染","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 虫卵在蚯蚓体内可存活4年多，在蚝蝓和蜗牛体内可存活1年以上，而野鸟则是隐性感染的带虫者。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":2,"end":4,"text":"伸颈","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":5,"end":9,"text":"张口呼吸","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":10,"end":14,"text":"左右甩头","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":3,"end":4,"text":"颈","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":6,"end":7,"text":"口","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":13,"end":14,"text":"头","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 病鸡伸颈，张口呼吸，左右甩头，甩出的分泌物中带有虫体。

label: [{"start":2,"end":6,"text":"食欲减少","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"废绝","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":12,"end":16,"text":"精神萎靡","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"衰弱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"消瘦","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":25,"end":29,"text":"呼吸困难","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":30,"end":34,"text":"窒息而死","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 初期食欲减少，继而废绝，精神萎靡，衰弱，消瘦，最后呼吸困难、窒息而死。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"幼鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 幼鸡感染后死亡率几乎达100%。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"成年鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":4,"end":8,"text":"比翼线虫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 成年鸡对比翼线虫的抵抗力强，症状一般不明显。

label: [{"start":4,"end":8,"text":"气管炎症","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"炎症","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"肺炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":12,"end":15,"text":"肺溢血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"溢血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":27,"text":"大叶性肺炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"气管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":12,"end":13,"text":"肺","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 剖检可见气管炎症、肺炎、肺溢血，严重时可见有大叶性肺炎。

label: [{"start":2,"end":5,"text":"病死鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":10,"end":14,"text":"气管黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 剖检病死鸡，若发现在气管黏膜上附着有虫体即可确诊。

label: [{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"碘溶液","labels":["drug"]},{"start":8,"end":10,"text":"碘片","labels":["drug"]},{"start":15,"end":18,"text":"碘化钾","labels":["drug"]},{"start":37,"end":39,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":53,"end":57,"text":"气管注射","labels":["control"]},{"start":58,"end":64,"text":"用细胶管灌服","labels":["control"]}]
text: (1)碘溶液。将碘片1.0g、碘化钾1.5g、蒸馏水1500mL配成溶液，雏鸡每只1.0~1.5mL,进行气管注射或用细胶管灌服。

label: [{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"噻苯唑","labels":["drug"]},{"start":22,"end":27,"text":"一次性口服","labels":["control"]},{"start":43,"end":47,"text":"拌料喂服","labels":["control"]}]
text: (2)噻苯唑。按每千克体重0.3～1.5g,一次性口服，或按0.05%~0.1%的比例拌料喂服，连用10~14天。

label: [{"start":3,"end":7,"text":"甲苯咪唑","labels":["drug"]},{"start":19,"end":26,"text":"混入饲料中喂服","labels":["control"]}]
text: (3)甲苯咪唑。按0.0125%的比例混入饲料中喂服，连用3天。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"搞好环境卫生","labels":["control"]},{"start":7,"end":14,"text":"粪便应及时清除","labels":["control"]},{"start":16,"end":20,"text":"堆积发酵","labels":["control"]},{"start":34,"end":41,"text":"鸡舍应保持干燥","labels":["control"]},{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"粪便","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":24,"end":28,"text":"比翼线虫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 搞好环境卫生，粪便应及时清除，并堆积发酵，以杀灭比翼线虫卵及其幼虫。鸡舍应保持干燥。

label: [{"start":6,"end":13,"text":"窝笼应经常消毒","labels":["control"]},{"start":25,"end":30,"text":"预防性驱虫","labels":["control"]},{"start":31,"end":40,"text":"严格控制鸡啄食蚯蚓","labels":["control"]},{"start":47,"end":58,"text":"雏鸡和成年鸡需分群饲养","labels":["control"]},{"start":35,"end":36,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":47,"end":49,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":50,"end":53,"text":"成年鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 饲具、栖架、窝笼应经常消毒。在流行地区，每年应进行预防性驱虫，严格控制鸡啄食蚯蚓、蛄蝓和蜗牛。雏鸡和成年鸡需分群饲养。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"鸡异刺线虫病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":8,"end":16,"text":"异刺科异刺属线虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":31,"end":36,"text":"鸡盲肠虫病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":44,"end":48,"text":"鸡线虫病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":19,"end":20,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"盲肠","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 鸡异刺线虫病是由异刺科异刺属线虫寄生于鸡的盲肠内引起的，故又称鸡盲肠虫病，是我国最常见的鸡线虫病。

label: [{"start":5,"end":6,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":15,"end":19,"text":"组织滴虫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 该虫除能使鸡致病外，其虫卵还是组织滴虫的传播者。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"异刺线虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"粪便","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":56,"end":57,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":61,"end":63,"text":"小肠","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":71,"end":73,"text":"盲肠","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":77,"end":80,"text":"盲肠壁","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":90,"end":92,"text":"肠腔","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 异刺线虫雌虫所产的卵，随粪便排出体外，在适宜的温度(18~26℃)和湿度的条件下，发育为含有幼虫的感染性虫卵，被鸡吞食后在小肠孵出幼虫，移行到盲肠后，钻入盲肠壁内发育一个时期，重返肠腔，发育为成虫。

label: [{"start":3,"end":4,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":12,"end":16,"text":"异刺线虫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 此外，鸡还可通过吃进含有异刺线虫卵的蚯蚓而遭受感染。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"患鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":32,"end":35,"text":"成年鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":2,"end":4,"text":"下痢","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":5,"end":9,"text":"食欲不振","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"消瘦","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"贫血","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":18,"end":22,"text":"发育受阻","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":35,"end":40,"text":"产蛋量下降","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":41,"end":43,"text":"停产","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 患鸡下痢，食欲不振，消瘦，贫血，雏鸡发育受阻，严重时可造成死亡。成年鸡产蛋量下降或停产。

label: [{"start":6,"end":10,"text":"盲肠肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":8,"end":10,"text":"肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":11,"end":15,"text":"肠壁发炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"发炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"增厚","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":23,"text":"黏膜出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"溃疡","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":28,"end":37,"text":"盲肠中部可发现虫体","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"盲肠","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":11,"end":13,"text":"肠壁","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":28,"end":32,"text":"盲肠中部","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 剖检时可见其盲肠肿大，肠壁发炎和增厚，黏膜出血、溃疡，在盲肠中部可发现虫体。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"鸡异刺线虫病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 鸡异刺线虫病的确诊需要粪检虫卵或剖检查到大量虫体。

label: [{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"蛔虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":11,"end":15,"text":"异刺线虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"蛔虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":26,"end":29,"text":"鸡蛔虫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 需注意与蛔虫卵的区别，异刺线虫卵和蛔虫卵很相似，仅比鸡蛔虫卵略小些。

label: [{"start":3,"end":7,"text":"丙硫咪唑","labels":["drug"]},{"start":22,"end":27,"text":"一次性饲喂","labels":["control"]},{"start":28,"end":37,"text":"混入饲料中让鸡自食","labels":["control"]},{"start":34,"end":35,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: (1)丙硫咪唑。按每千克体重30~35mg,一次性饲喂或混入饲料中让鸡自食。

label: [{"start":3,"end":7,"text":"左旋咪唑","labels":["drug"]},{"start":22,"end":26,"text":"自由饮水","labels":["control"]}]
text: (2)左旋咪唑。按每千克体重25~35mg,自由饮水，隔2~3周再用1次。

label: [{"start":51,"end":56,"text":"一次性饲喂","labels":["control"]},{"start":3,"end":8,"text":"硫化二苯胺","labels":["drug"]},{"start":9,"end":12,"text":"吩噻嗪","labels":["drug"]},{"start":14,"end":17,"text":"成年鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":33,"end":35,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: (3)硫化二苯胺(吩噻嗪)。成年鸡按每千克体重0.5~1.0mg,雏鸡按每千克体重0.3~0.5mg,一次性饲喂。

label: [{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"噻咪啶","labels":["drug"]},{"start":18,"end":22,"text":"直接投服","labels":["control"]},{"start":23,"end":32,"text":"混入饲料中让鸡自食","labels":["control"]},{"start":29,"end":30,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: (4)噻咪啶。按每千克体重15mg,直接投服或混入饲料中让鸡自食。

label: [{"start":2,"end":8,"text":"每日清扫鸡舍","labels":["control"]},{"start":9,"end":15,"text":"粪便堆积发酵","labels":["control"]},{"start":18,"end":19,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"粪便","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 平时每日清扫鸡舍，粪便堆积发酵，防止鸡吞食感染性虫卵。

label: [{"start":2,"end":12,"text":"注意清除鸡舍内的蚯蚓","labels":["control"]}]
text: 同时注意清除鸡舍内的蚯蚓；

label: [{"start":0,"end":10,"text":"雏鸡与成年鸡分群饲养","labels":["control"]},{"start":14,"end":20,"text":"每年定期驱虫","labels":["control"]},{"start":39,"end":44,"text":"预防性驱虫","labels":["control"]},{"start":48,"end":52,"text":"鸡蛔虫病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":23,"end":29,"text":"鸡异刺线虫病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"成年鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]}]
text: 雏鸡与成年鸡分群饲养，对鸡群每年定期驱虫，由于鸡异刺线虫病无明显的季节性，所以预防性驱虫可以结合鸡蛔虫病的时间进行。
